sequenceDiagram
    participant Cliente
    participant API as API de creación
    participant Limiter as Rate limiter
    participant Gen as Generador base62
    participant Store as Repositorio
    participant Cache as Caché

    Cliente->>API: crear(long_url, owner)
    API->>Limiter: verificar cuota del owner
    Limiter-->>API: permitido
    API->>Gen: siguiente código
    Gen-->>API: code
    API->>Store: guardar code -> long_url
    Store-->>API: ShortLink
    API-->>Cliente: short_url

    Cliente->>Cache: resolver(code)
    alt cache hit
        Cache-->>Cliente: long_url
    else cache miss
        Cache->>Store: buscar(code)
        Store-->>Cache: long_url
        Cache-->>Cliente: long_url
    end
